0.4.2

When bumping version, update in these files:
==============================================

1. VERSION (this file)
2. memory-plugin/.claude-plugin/plugin.json
3. .claude-plugin/marketplace.json
4. memory-plugin/README.md (## Version section + add changelog entry)

Format: semantic versioning (MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH)
- MAJOR: Breaking changes
- MINOR: New features, backward compatible
- PATCH: Bug fixes, improvements
